After we organize the data into its category directory, we then 
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
1. First step: use weka to produce the text based arff file
java weka.core.converters.TextDirectoryLoader -dir /media/1Tnewdisk/intention_routing/lyrics/NTWICM_lyrics_wiki/ > /media/1Tnewdisk/intention_routing/arff/stereomood_angry_calm_happy_sad_text_NTWICM.arff


2. Process the arff file into our data format.
 sh arff_to_icsiboostdata.sh

3. Then we can directly run our experiment
icsiboost -n 1000 -S boost
